title: 750. Reaction to Patriots vs. Bills Game, Breaking Down the CFP & Mario Cristobal to Miami
itunes:title: 750. Reaction to Patriots vs. Bills Game, Breaking Down the CFP & Mario Cristobal to Miami
description:
Rhett Lewis and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys react to the New England Patriots vs. Buffalo Bills Monday Night Football game. After that, the duo break down the College Football Playoff semifinal matchups. Then, the pair discuss Mario Cristobal leaving Oregon for Miami and to wrap up, give potential coaching candidates for the vacant Oregon head coaching job.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
